      "title": "MySQUAR - Senior NodeJS/PGSQL - HCMC - FT",
      "description": "## Location\n- Saigon, Vietnam (394 Vo Van Kiet, D1, HCMC)\n## Salary Expectation (A.k.a. Perks)\n- Love from the team\n- A competitive salary (baseline of 1000$ for mid-range)\n- Full health benefits and social insurance\n- A training budget\n- A macbook and a 21\" screen\n- ESOP\n- Possible travel to Myanmar to meet users and the team as well as Singapore\n- Lots of cool stuff to relax (who said Foosball?)\n## Requirements\n- Mid-level to Senior Position\n- Ability to grow, learn, challenge and be challenged \n- NodeJS\n- PostgreSQL\n- Knowledge of Graph and OrientDB is a plus\n- A lot of passion and a good mind\n## Skills\n### Must Have\n- Rock solid NodeJS skills\n- PGSQL\n- Know your s\\* about patterns, scalable code, debugging, optimization, etc...\n### We need you to\n\nWork on a highly scalable backend, own your code, work in team and produce the best code you're ever written (yet). \n### You can bring\n- Attention to details, quality and user-centric work\n- Good attitude\n- Passion\n### Contact\n\nNicolas Embleton: nico@mysquar.com\nOr apply at http://vietnam.mysquar.com",
